    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. Honestly, it\u2019s in pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in the garage. It looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for a new adventure, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
