    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of BMW M-Division engineering. This example features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec dampening and refreshed bushings, ensuring the car\u2019s original turn-in characteristics remain sharp. This is a mechanically flawless, collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
