    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle presents in a state indistinguishable from the day it left the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. The factory alloy wheels are absolutely pristine, free of any curb rash, and are wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory-fresh scent. The premium leather upholstery is supple, without a single crease or sign of wear, and the high-definition infotainment screens remain crystal clear and scratch-free. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive logbook documenting every scheduled maintenance interval. It has been stored in a climate-controlled garage under a breathable car cover and has never seen inclement weather. This sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. For the buyer seeking perfection without compromise, this is the one.",
